                        <msItem class="#funerary.epitaph" ana="#jewish">
                            <p>Zoora, 24 July 469? CE. Tombstone. Funerary (Epitaph).</p>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
                    <!--  *************************************  <physDesc>  ********************************* -->
                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc ana="#tombstone">
                            <supportDesc ana="#stone.other">
                                <support>
                                    <p>Local sandstone, almost square in shape with tapered bottom,
                                        chipped all around</p>
                                    <dimensions type="surface" unit="cm">
                                        <height>30</height>
                                        <width>27</width>
                                        <depth/>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </support>
                                <condition ana="#complete">
                                    <p>The front surface is now eroded especially in its lower part
                                        with partial effacement of the decoration</p>
                                </condition>
                            </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
                                <layout columns="1" writtenLines="10">
                                    <p>A miscalculation of the inscribed area is obvious in the
                                        unequal distribution of the text. The first six lines are
                                        very crowded, the following two present a big interlinear
                                        space, while the remaning two are accommodated in the area
                                        below the decoration</p>
                                </layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
                        </objectDesc>
                        <!--  *************************************  <handDesc>  *********************************  -->
                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote ana="#impressed.inscribed">
                                <p>Out of ten lines, the first six are incised, while the remaining
                                    for are painted in red. The letter are small, rather carefully
                                    executed and aligned</p>
                            </handNote>
                        </handDesc>
                        <!--  *************************************  <decoDesc>  *********************************  -->
                        <decoDesc>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Faint traces of a central candelabrum</ab>
                                <locus>Beneath the epitaph, from which it is separated by a incised
                                    horizontal line</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Two stylized birds facing right</ab>
                                <locus>Flanking the candelabrum on either side</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Deeply engraved linear frame, with the upper horizontal and the
                                    right vertical line projecting</ab>
                                <locus>Surrounding inscription and symbols</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                        </decoDesc>
